{"tid":2363072,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奧布萊恩：華府考慮行動回應香港民主派被捕事件","createTime":"2021-01-12T02:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T04:11:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a6b5b2ae8ebcc221f7a03ca88618c745fe663f","tid":2363072,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T02:52:40.000Z","msg":"美國安顧問稱華府考慮行動回應香港民主派被捕事件<br />\n<br />\n美國國家安全顧問奧布萊恩表示，華府正考慮採取進一步行動，回應50多名香港民主派人士被捕的事件。<br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩發表聲明，指特朗普政府去年5月已經預見並宣告香港這個自由開放的社會，死於中國共產黨手上，形容今次事件是北京在香港民主的棺木上，再釘上新一口釘，全球各國必須追究北京的責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569928-20210112.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569928-20210112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJucF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=feadcc93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569928-20210112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5e51c045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569928-20210112.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2d7709018ff429c8a0af6dcc3d49524e672da404","tid":2363072,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T02:53:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>考慮</strong></span>"},{"pid":"919f2dcde460bd9026ae46e698eb25d2478d1320","tid":2363072,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T02:59:13.000Z","msg":"算吧啦"},{"pid":"a56fc941ffd9ad47ea32e574c1e233c1b3032595","tid":2363072,"uid":150427,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T03:05:02.000Z","msg":"Talk is cheap..."},{"pid":"bf772b4f4ef1dd5ccdb81ac2c503790e91f85b78","tid":2363072,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"越制裁越拉得勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no